name: Pop Art Cats by Matt Chessco

metadata.name: Pop Art Cats #2
metadata.description: A community-driven collectibles project featuring art by Matt Chessco. This project is your entry in the pop art world. Three more NFT collections will follow. 20% of all the royalties made from secondary sales will go to the Pop Art Community Treasury. Holders will vote for experiences, activations and projects that will benefit the Pop Art Community.
